-- Bertelsmann Buys R2M, Rights to 12,000 Songs, Handelsblatt Says
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-02-29T19:20:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-29/bertelsmann-buys-r2m-rights-to-12-000-songs-handelsblatt-says.html
Bertelsmann AG,  Europe ’s largest
media group, will buy R2M Music of the U.S. and its rights to
12,000 songs for a “mid-two-digit million-euro” amount,
 Handelsblatt  reported in a preview of an article to be published
tomorrow, without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
